dct_title_s: Geologic map of the Taft and Mouth of Kern quadrangles, Kern County, California
dct_alternative_sm: Taft and Mouth of Kern map
dct_description_sm: by Thomas W. Dibblee, Jr. ; edited by John A. Minch.
Relief shown by contours and spot heights.
"Topographic base map from available USGS 7.5-minute quadrangle TAFT, CA 1973, AMA (i.e. AMS) 2154 III NE -- Series V895; MOUTH OF KERN, CA 1973, 2154 III NW -- Series V895."
Includes quadrangle location map, index to adjacent 7.5 minute quadrangles, and index to sources of geology.
